### Card / Panel → Card

**React Web:**

```tsx
<div className="border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-4 bg-white">
    <h3 className="font-bold">{product.name}</h3>
    <p className="text-gray-500">${product.price}</p>
</div>
```

**GlueStack:**

```tsx
import { Card, Heading, Text } from '@gluestack-ui/themed';

<Card size="md" variant="elevated" p="$4">
    <Heading size="md">{product.name}</Heading>
    <Text color="$coolGray500" mt="$1">${product.price.toFixed(2)}</Text>
</Card>
```

