## Alert / Toast

**GlueStack Alert:**

```tsx
import { Alert, AlertIcon, AlertText, InfoIcon } from '@gluestack-ui/themed';

<Alert action="info">
    <AlertIcon as={InfoIcon} mr="$2" />
    <AlertText>Your changes have been saved.</AlertText>
</Alert>
```

`action` values: `"info"` | `"success"` | `"warning"` | `"error"` | `"muted"`

**GlueStack Toast (programmatic):**

```tsx
import { useToast, Toast, ToastTitle, ToastDescription } from '@gluestack-ui/themed';

const toast = useToast();

const showSuccess = () => {
    toast.show({
        placement: 'top',
        render: ({ id }) => (
            <Toast action="success" id={id}>
                <ToastTitle>Saved!</ToastTitle>
                <ToastDescription>Your product was created.</ToastDescription>
            </Toast>
        ),
    });
};
```

