## Spacing & Sizing Tokens

GlueStack uses `$` prefix for design tokens:

| Tailwind | GlueStack Token |
|----------|----------------|
| `p-1` (4px) | `p="$1"` |
| `p-2` (8px) | `p="$2"` |
| `p-4` (16px) | `p="$4"` |
| `p-6` (24px) | `p="$6"` |
| `mt-2` | `mt="$2"` |
| `mb-4` | `mb="$4"` |
| `gap-3` | `space="sm"` (on VStack/HStack) |
| `rounded` | `borderRadius="$sm"` |
| `rounded-xl` | `borderRadius="$xl"` |
| `rounded-full` | `borderRadius="$full"` |
| `bg-white` | `bg="$white"` |
| `text-blue-600` | `color="$primary600"` |

