## Best Practices

1. **Use `FormControl`** for all form fields — it handles label, error, required state in one wrapper
2. **Use `VStack`/`HStack`** instead of `Box` with manual `flexDirection` — more readable
3. **Use `ButtonSpinner`** inside `Button` for loading states — built-in alignment
4. **Use Toast** for mutation success/error feedback — replaces browser `alert()`
5. **Use `$` token system** for spacing/colors — avoids magic numbers and stays consistent with the theme
6. **Use `isInvalid`/`isDisabled`/`isRequired`** props on `Input` and `FormControl` — drives accessible state automatically
7. **Wrap root in `GluestackUIProvider`** — components will not render without it
8. **Use `Modal` with `ModalBackdrop`** — the backdrop handles dismiss on press automatically
9. **Use `Select` not native `Picker`** — GlueStack Select looks consistent on both iOS and Android
10. **Keep custom styles minimal** — if you're writing `StyleSheet.create`, check if GlueStack has a component first

---

## Migration Checklist

- [ ] Install GlueStack UI: `npx gluestack-ui init`
- [ ] Wrap root layout with `GluestackUIProvider`
- [ ] Replace `div` (column) → `VStack` or `Box`
- [ ] Replace `div` (row) → `HStack`
- [ ] Replace `h1..h6` → `Heading size="..."`
- [ ] Replace `p` / `span` → `Text size="..."`
- [ ] Replace `<button>` → `<Button><ButtonText>`
- [ ] Replace `<input type="text">` → `<Input><InputField>`
- [ ] Replace `<textarea>` → `<Textarea><TextareaInput>`
- [ ] Replace `<select>` → `<Select>` with portal/content/items
- [ ] Replace form field wrappers → `<FormControl>` with label + error
- [ ] Replace custom modal divs → `<Modal>` with backdrop/content/header/footer
- [ ] Replace custom spinner → `<Spinner>`
- [ ] Replace custom badges → `<Badge><BadgeText>`
- [ ] Replace `alert()` / toast library → GlueStack `useToast`
- [ ] Replace `<hr>` → `<Divider>`
- [ ] Replace padding/margin inline styles → `$` token props (`p="$4"`, `mt="$2"`)
- [ ] Replace hardcoded colors → `$` color tokens (`color="$primary600"`)
- [ ] Add `colorMode` to `GluestackUIProvider` for dark mode support
- [ ] Test all components on both iOS and Android

